Looking at QB efficiency prior to Week 4 and found some interesting things
- Top tier of Lamar, Mahomes, Allen now joined by Hurts, Tua, and... Trevor Lawrence?
- Baker has been quite bad
- Cooper Rush is right around average
#nflverse https://t.co/oykanJjmEL

2022 version of gunslingers vs game managers below focusing largely on play style, baker can't do anything right

Through 4 weeks, here's how well each team has moved the ball on scripted plays vs non scripted plays. 
#nflverse https://t.co/qtiQFHfSQI

QB play to start the season has regressed from what we are accustomed to seeing. Baker, Kyler, Wilson and Cousins have experienced the largest drops in efficiency.

A few QBs to see an increase in production this year include; Hurts, Lawrence, Lamar, and Allen. 

#nflverse https://t.co/h6APvuRUEA

The #Ravens are still outperforming their series conversion rate by being 1st in the NFL in explosive play rate.
Also the #Jaguars are slowly becoming a top offense
